INSERT INTO `h_images_content` VALUES (16,113,'&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;在即将到来的5G时代及各类光电资讯产业的蓬勃发展下，光通讯与光资讯相关技术及产品需求越来越广泛，海威华芯在经过多年的技术开发之後， 已具备具备2-6磷化铟、砷化镓的光电代工能力，用于人脸识别、光纤通讯、5G等，可以确保产品品质符合客户及市场的需求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;随着苹果手机使用VCSEL技术进行面部识别，国际上越来越重视该技术，未来该技术还将用于自动驾驶、人工智能等领域，市场潜力巨大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576832836,1576832836,'/uploads/allimg/20191220/2-1912201FG4J6.png'),(17,114,'&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;在即将到来的5G时代及各类光电资讯产业的蓬勃发展下，光通讯与光资讯相关技术及产品需求越来越广泛，海威华芯在经过多年的技术开发之後， 已具备具备2-6磷化铟、砷化镓的光电代工能力，用于人脸识别、光纤通讯、5G等，可以确保产品品质符合客户及市场的需求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;随着苹果手机使用VCSEL技术进行面部识别，国际上越来越重视该技术，未来该技术还将用于自动驾驶、人工智能等领域，市场潜力巨大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576830099,1576830099,''),(18,115,'&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;在即将到来的5G时代及各类光电资讯产业的蓬勃发展下，光通讯与光资讯相关技术及产品需求越来越广泛，海威华芯在经过多年的技术开发之後， 已具备具备2-6磷化铟、砷化镓的光电代工能力，用于人脸识别、光纤通讯、5G等，可以确保产品品质符合客户及市场的需求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;随着苹果手机使用VCSEL技术进行面部识别，国际上越来越重视该技术，未来该技术还将用于自动驾驶、人工智能等领域，市场潜力巨大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576830104,1576830104,''),(19,123,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;海威华芯从发展之初到现在，已获得30项荣誉资质，得到了国家及社会各界的支持。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576633416,1576633416,''),(20,124,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;成都海威华芯科技有限公司是国内主要提供六吋砷化镓/氮化镓微波集成电路(GaAs/GaＮ MMIC)的晶圆代工（Foundry）和设计服务的企业。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;海威华芯拥有完整的技术团队，先进的GaAs/GaN集成电路制造技术和生产设备，其六吋GaAs/GaＮ集成电路Foundry线达到业内先进水平。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;华夏芯，海之威——公司提供稳定、可靠、开放、优质的化合物半导体设计和加工服务。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;在射频微波领域，公司更专注于提供GaAs pHEMT、HBT和GaN HEMT集成电路制程，为客户提供全面多样的解决模型，助力客户快速发展。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576726183,1576726183,'/uploads/allimg/20191216/2-191216162643a4.png'),(21,125,'&lt;p&gt;Chengdu Haiwei Huaxin Technology Co., Ltd. is a domestic enterprise that mainly provides foundry and design services for 6-inch GaAs / GaN MMIC integrated circuits (GaAs / GaN MMIC).Haiwei Huaxin has a complete technical team, advanced GaAs / GaN integrated circuit manufacturing technology and production equipment, and its six-inch GaAs / GaN integrated circuit Foundry line has reached the advanced level in the industry.Huaxiaxin, Haizhiwei-the company provides stable, reliable, open, high-quality compound semiconductor design and processing services.In the field of radio frequency microwave, the company is more focused on providing GaAs pHEMT, HBT and GaN HEMT integrated circuit manufacturing processes, providing customers with comprehensive and diverse solution models to help customers develop rapidly.&lt;/p&gt;',1576570359,1576570359,''),(22,126,'&lt;p&gt;Chengdu Haiwei Huaxin Technology Co., Ltd., located in Tianfu New District, is the first domestic manufacturer to provide pure wafer foundry services for 6-inch GaAs MMICs.Haiwei Huaxin has a complete technical team, advanced GaAs integrated circuit manufacturing technology and production equipment. Its &amp;quot;six-inch GaAs integrated circuit Foundry line&amp;quot; is a key industrialization project supported by the country, and has important strategic significance at home and abroad.&lt;/p&gt;',1576650884,1576650884,''),(23,127,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;海威华芯以先进的化合物半导体制造技术为本，坚持精益求精的理念，追求细节和零缺陷，通过全员创新及持续改善，提供卓越品质的产品与服务，达成客户的全面满意。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;system&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191218/2-19121Q04Z1509.png&quot; title=&quot;品质管理&quot; alt=&quot;品质管理&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;',1576648021,1576648021,''),(24,128,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Haiwei Huaxin is based on advanced compound semiconductor manufacturing technology, adheres to the concept of excellence, pursues details and zero defects, and provides superior quality products and services through full staff innovation and continuous improvement to achieve customer satisfaction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;system&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191218/2-19121Q04Z1509.png&quot; title=&quot;品质管理&quot; alt=&quot;品质管理&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;',1576650825,1576650825,''),(25,129,'&lt;p&gt;Operating in an environmentally and socially responsible and positive manner, dedicated to new semiconductor manufacturing, we always comply with applicable regulations and customer requirements.Taking clean production and zero disasters as our social responsibility.The company has advanced facilities and management team in pollution prevention, energy saving and emission reduction, disaster prevention and other aspects.It is expected that through continuous improvement activities, employees&amp;#39; environmental, safety and health awareness will be stimulated, and the company&amp;#39;s operational risk management will be strengthened to ensure the company&amp;#39;s sustainable development.And strive to be a first-class enterprise in the society and coexist with environmentally friendly ...&lt;/p&gt;',1576833437,1576833437,''),(26,130,'&lt;p class=&quot;tt&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(190, 107, 0); line-height: 30px; font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;海威华芯以对环境和社会负责任和积极影响的方式运作，致力于新型半导体制造。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;env&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;我们始终遵守适用的法规和客户要求。以清洁生产和零灾害作为本公司的社会责任。公司在污染防治、节能减排、灾害预防等方面拥有先进的设施设备和管理团队。 期望通过持续改善的活动，激发员工环境、安全与健康意识，强化公司的营运风险管理，确保公司的可持续发展。并力做到社会一流企业，与环境友好共存。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576651400,1576651400,''),(27,131,'&lt;p&gt;Chengdu Haiwei Huaxin is based on advanced compound semiconductor manufacturing technology, adheres to the concept of excellence, pursues details and zero defects, provides innovative products and services through full innovation and continuous improvement, and achieves customers&amp;#39; full satisfaction ......&lt;/p&gt;',1576736929,1576736929,'/uploads/allimg/20191219/2-191219112Z4222.png'),(28,132,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(27, 27, 27); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;成都海威华芯以先进的化合物半导体制造技术为本，坚持精益求精的理念，追求细节和零缺陷，通过全员创新及持续改善，提供卓越品质的产品与服务，达成客户的全面满意......&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576726147,1576726147,'/uploads/allimg/20191219/2-191219112Z4222.png'),(31,135,'&lt;p&gt;2015年6月，四川省信息和安全委员会授予我司四川省信息安全产业重点培育企业称号。 信息安全产业是保障国家信息安全的战略性核心产业。加快发展信息安全产业是进一步贯彻落实中央和省委、省政府决策部署， 保障信息安全、推进信息化和信息产业发展的重要举措，我司将抓住产业基础和优势，布局长远发展，积蓄发展后劲。&lt;/p&gt;',1576743683,1576743683,''),(32,136,'&lt;p&gt;海威华芯拥有国际一流的半导体工艺设备，包括：步进式光刻机、离子注入机、金属溅射台、金属蒸发台、湿法蚀刻台等，设备稳定性高，性能优越。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;作为国内首家提供六英吋砷化镓/氮化镓微波集成电路（GaAs/GaN MMIC）晶圆代工服务的公司，目前已开发出PPA25、PPA15、IPD、PPA25ED、HBT02、 NPA25等工艺且已经小批量跑线运行。 海威华芯是军民融合、混合所有制改革与供给侧结构性改革的先驱企业，已走在全国前列！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;国企的技术与市场优势、上市企业的资金与管理优势，做到军、民实力、资金、管理的深度融合。在中国射频微波领域，四川排名第一位，海威华芯与电子科技大学等高校已建立战略合作关系， 引入行业内高端技术人才，已成功培育出一批具有行业引领性的技术团队，为稳固海威华芯技术能力优势打下了良好的基础。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576726250,1576726250,'/uploads/allimg/20191218/2-19121Q1333B23.png'),(33,137,'&lt;p&gt;In June 2015, Sichuan Provincial Information and Security Commission awarded our company the title of Key Cultivation Enterprise of Sichuan Information Security Industry.The information security industry is a strategic core industry that guarantees national information security.Accelerating the development of the information security industry is an important measure to further implement the decision-making and deployment of the central and provincial Party committees and governments to ensure information security and promote the development of information technology and the information industry.stamina.&lt;/p&gt;',1576743699,1576743699,''),(38,142,'&lt;p&gt;Haiwei Huaxin has world-class semiconductor process equipment, including: stepper lithography machines, ion implanters, metal sputtering stations, metal evaporation stations, wet etching stations, etc., with high stability and superior performance.As the first domestic company to provide wafer foundry services for six-inch gallium arsenide / gallium nitride microwave integrated circuits (GaAs / GaN MMIC), it has developed PPA25, PPA15, IPD, PPA25ED, HBT02, NPA25 and other processesAlready run in small batches.Haiwei Huaxin is a pioneer in military-civilian integration, mixed ownership reform and supply-side structural reform, and has been at the forefront of the country!The technological and market advantages of state-owned enterprises and the capital and management advantages of listed companies have achieved a deep integration of military and civilian strength, capital and management.In the field of radio frequency and microwave in China, Sichuan ranks first. Highway Huaxin has established strategic partnerships with universities such as the University of Electronic Science and Technology, introduced high-end technical talents in the industry, and has successfully cultivated a number of industry-leading technical teams.It has laid a good foundation for solidifying the advantages of Haiwei Huaxin&amp;#39;s technical capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;',1576833349,1576833349,'/uploads/allimg/20191218/2-19121Q1333B23.png'),(43,147,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;海威华芯拥有多项GaAs自主知识产权&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;经过多年的技术研发、积累，已形成多项发明专利、实用新型专利、外观专利。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576737180,1576737180,''),(44,148,'&lt;p&gt;Haiwei Huaxin has a number of GaAs independent intellectual property rights.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;After years of technology research and development and accumulation, it has formed a number of invention patents, utility model patents and appearance patents.&lt;/p&gt;',1576738105,1576738105,'/uploads/allimg/20191219/2-191219112Z4222.png'),(45,151,'&lt;p&gt;In the coming 5G era and the booming development of various optoelectronic information industries, the demand for optical communication and optical information-related technologies and products is becoming more and more extensive. After years of technology development, Highway Huaxin has been equipped with 2-6The optoelectronic foundry capabilities of indium phosphide and gallium arsenide are used for face recognition, fiber optic communication, 5G, etc., which can ensure that product quality meets customer and market requirements.As Apple phones use VCSEL technology for facial recognition, more and more attention is being paid to this technology internationally. In the future, this technology will also be used in areas such as autonomous driving and artificial intelligence, with huge market potential.&lt;/p&gt;',1576833223,1576833223,'/uploads/allimg/20191220/2-1912201FG4J6.png'),(46,152,'&lt;p&gt;Haiwei Huaxin already has 6-inch gallium arsenide 0.15μm pHEMT technology, 0.25μm power pHEMT technology, 0.25μm E / D technology, IPD integrated passive, 2μm HBT technology foundry capability&lt;/p&gt;',1576651727,1576651727,''),(47,153,'&lt;p&gt;Haiwei Huaxin already has 6-inch gallium arsenide 0.15μm pHEMT technology, 0.25μm power pHEMT technology, 0.25μm E / D technology, IPD integrated passive, 2μm HBT technology foundry capability&lt;/p&gt;',1576651763,1576651763,''),(48,157,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;截止2019年3月，供共获得发明专利276项&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576724727,1576724727,''),(49,158,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;截止2019年3月，供共获得实用新型专利352项&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576724746,1576724746,'')