: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;海威华芯每年制定减废减排等环保方案，切实减少废弃物产生及污染物排放；同时开展节能项目，降低能耗。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cont_img&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 27.8281px 67.4844px 0px 92.7969px; text-align: center; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); padding-top: 20px;&quot;&gt;水资源消耗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191219/2-1912191I34H36.png&quot; title=&quot;环保执行情况(图2)&quot; alt=&quot;2-1912191I34H36.png&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;max-width: 100% !important; height: auto !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); padding-top: 20px;&quot;&gt;废气排放情况&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191219/2-1912191I3552T.png&quot; title=&quot;环保执行情况(图4)&quot; alt=&quot;2-1912191I3552T.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); padding-top: 20px;&quot;&gt;废弃物管理&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191219/2-1912191I401E5.png&quot; title=&quot;环保执行情况(图6)&quot; alt=&quot;2-1912191I401E5.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576748169,1576748169,''),(75,184,'&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Highway Huaxin not only pays attention to the development of enterprises and creates economic value, but also emphasizes the prevention of environmental pollution and the good use of resources and energy.We implement continuous improvement measures, fulfill environmental protection responsibilities, and promote sustainable development.1. Improve the design of pollution control and meet or exceed national laws and regulations and international conventions.2. Implement the environmental management system and make every effort to maintain continuous improvement of environmental performance.3. Strengthen waste reduction and pollution prevention, make good use of and recycle resources, and achieve green design and production.4. Promote environmental education, improve the concept of environmental protection, and ensure that personnel at all levels perform their duties of environmental protection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(56, 56, 56); font-family: &amp;quot;microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://haiwei.io/uploads/ueditor/20191219/2-191219163649532.png&quot; title=&quot;环保方针政策(图1)&quot; alt=&quot;2-191219163649532.png&quot; width=&quot;860&quot; height=&quot;348&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;width: 860px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1576748949,1576748949,''),(76,185,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:100%!important;height:auto!important;max-width: 100% !important; height: auto !important; float: right;&quot; src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20191219/2-1912191A601H8.png&quot; title=&quot;环保理念(图1)&quot; alt=&quot;2-1912191A601H8